openvpn-dco-dkms (0.2.20260526-debian0) stable; urgency=medium

  * ovpn: fix 6.16 compat hack on RHEL 9.8 (Antonio Quartulli, 4081ec1)
  * ovpn-dco: compat hack for 7.1 about tcp_recvmsg changing signature (Antonio Quartulli, 65afbcb)
